Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.61,0:26:14.48,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏に流れだした
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.66,0:26:18.18,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}制服の群れに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.01,0:26:23.38,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}逆らうよに　自転車の
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.46,0:26:27.63,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}ペダル　思いきり踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.92,0:26:32.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放課後のグランドの脇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.35,0:26:35.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}金網をくぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.83,0:26:41.18,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年　見つけた　ひまわりは
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.29,0:26:45.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年より　誇らしげに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.73,0:26:49.17,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}空を見上げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.96,0:26:54.50,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}折れないように　枯れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.52,0:26:58.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}涙に出来たなら
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.91,0:27:05.21,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明日は何かが変わるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.89,0:27:12.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}雨降る日は　雨に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.30,0:27:16.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}あの　ひまわりみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.90,0:27:20.96,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}まっすぐ　背を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.20,0:27:27.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}今日は揺れていたって、いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.61,0:26:14.48,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黃昏下  逆行在流動的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.66,0:26:18.18,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}身著制服的人群中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.01,0:26:23.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}盡情地  蹬踩著
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.46,0:26:27.63,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}自行車的腳踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.92,0:26:32.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放學後  操場邊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.35,0:26:35.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}鑽過鐵絲網
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.83,0:26:41.18,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年發現的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.29,0:26:45.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}比以往還要驕傲地
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.73,0:26:49.17,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}仰望著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.96,0:26:54.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}不屈不撓  不會枯萎地
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.52,0:26:58.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}若是放聲哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.91,0:27:05.21,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明天又會變得怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.89,0:27:12.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}下雨的日子  在雨中搖擺
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.30,0:27:16.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}就像那朵向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.90,0:27:20.96,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}挺直了腰杆
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.20,0:27:27.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}哪怕今日有所動搖  也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  夕子她？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她非常討厭爸爸你的這個習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是問了朋友也只有你一個人這麼不乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子是那麼說的？對你？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.79,0:00:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  哥哥  那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些煙是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  也讓我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我說哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是園原基地的方向嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:05.73,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(268,360)\fs13\fr-8}園原基地周圍地區發生山林火災？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}剛才的煙和火災的紅光…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}在園原基地發生的爆炸是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水前寺邦博
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:22.94,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(480,360)\fs29}水前寺 請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事情相信大家都聽說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  今天課就上到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人馬上放學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我安靜！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了你們的安全著想才採取的措施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了這是緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下個返校日前就老老實實待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  淺羽  還有西久保
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上繞到哪裡去逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是河口讓我們儘早回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動鉛筆  一直在用的不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你好像也說\N橡皮擦還是尺什麼的不見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是馬上就會開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺羽  快來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正要去取材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  負責在我們的期刊上\N寫文章介紹美食商鋪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼類型都有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正要出去取材\N就想伊里野要不要也一塊去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  河口的話不用理會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是難得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野還一次都沒有\N進行過取材和撰寫報導吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟伊里野也是新聞社的社員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連淺羽的程度都做不到的話會很頭痛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去還是不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不戰而勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去的是蛋糕店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐巴士10分鐘左右的路程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙黃白毫和草莓芭菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晶穗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是在偷聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說是偷看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很甜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油泡芙和冰釀咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晶穗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美乃滋醬油義大利麵和奶油蘇打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晶穗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用小盤子盛來吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…取材吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點反胃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊  女生的甜食胃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我跟晶穗歸為一類啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野沒來參加學園祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野也來參加學園祭該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因為新聞社的企劃要出號外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和淺羽到處去取材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂「號外」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是和淺羽一起吃炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和淺羽一起吃烤地瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和淺羽一起在篝火晚會上跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後那一項…是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  去採訪下一家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多都吃得下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:07:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵人套餐一份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晶穗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是先說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店的鐵餐是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵人套餐一份！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和晶穗一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:17.67,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fs17}免費飲食列傳\N鐵人套餐\N價格四千日元\N（鐵人拉麵+鐵人餃子+鐵人中華大蓋飯）\N全部吃完則不收取費用\N限制時間六十分鐘\N中途離席、以及把四周弄得髒兮兮的情況下將直接結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鐵餐兩份！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,60分鐘內無法吃完時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子弄得髒兮兮時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就直接結束並收取4000日元的費用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  至少要吃掉一半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  將手離開桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部吃完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是鐵人餃子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將手離開桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙！ 燙燙燙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退後！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  真是場精彩的比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  看好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一定是這邊的短髮孩子贏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你沒看到她剛才都快要吐出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中華大蓋飯來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是本店的老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓如月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論結果如何這都是最後一盤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望兩位都不要留下任何遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼將手離開桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是老大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該醫生叫停了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會輸給晶穗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對…不會輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗  加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野別輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃啊！  吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  醒著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很怕…你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我一起去取材的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕得腿發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得一定會被帶到沒人的地方\N然後痛打一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我逃走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得是我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很怕你  但我怎麼能認輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一直都這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從最初見到你開始直到剛才  我都很怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胃藥買來了  胃藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破最低年齡記錄了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈噗 「噗」的流出鼻血來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  那個「加奈噗」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我胃藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野也要吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊？  這個大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼下午沒有打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我硬邀她一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來！  你到底是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 那是加奈噗的哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體情況我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我介紹說是姓榎本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  淺羽之前遇到過這個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  實際聊過後覺得是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是很關心伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.82,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈噗  你染髪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.10,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是淡銀灰色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.10,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(334,441)\fs20}platinum blonde
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.92,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形象改變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.57,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.47,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回座…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.82,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:16.56,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  不是的  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:17.51,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:18.54,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃開！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.62,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.52,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.66,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候染這麼個頭髮算什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.45,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個並不是特意染的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:31.06,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  雖然我們也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:31.89,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:37.74,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  伊里野一直都在吃很多藥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.66,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是藥的副作用…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.41,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就染回來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.35,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  站起來  到辦公室去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.73,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}伊里野加奈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:51.15,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}田中先生來電
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.49,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}請你速到辦公室來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.03,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}伊里野加奈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.46,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}請你速到辦公室來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.53,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:09.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.33,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才是第一節課
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣來學校不就沒意義了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:23.56,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.25,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:35.38,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把報紙抽走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.63,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:40.56,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連天氣預報都沒有  真頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.91,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs18}致各位觀眾\N\N現在，將依\N照國土防衛\N新法對情報\N進行管制。\N根據有事對\N策準則非法\N使用電波將\N構成重大違\N法行為。\N自衛軍治安\N部隊也正在\N加強對非官\N方廣播的取\N締工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:43.30,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是情報管制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐角的坂井先生好像也要被疏散了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才來告過別了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.77,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變冷清了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:59.22,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}安靜！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:58.92,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 晶穗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:01.57,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  所以和花村一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.63,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽從父母請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她還說托你照顧伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.04,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  簡直像是幼稚園的保育員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.96,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  原來你在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:36.99,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.35,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.83,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見  我看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:43.97,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:45.14,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.04,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:46.94,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.58,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:50.73,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.72,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說的話  那就不要說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:02.43,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說也行的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:05.30,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:23.01,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:43.45,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時看得見  有時看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:45.58,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種突發性的視覺異常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.74,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是從現在才開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:50.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這麼嚴重倒還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:55.24,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這樣了為什麼還要來學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.59,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.65,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是「淺羽袋」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:16.40,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  她是把這些東西當作護身符吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:24.29,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管去哪裡不管做什麼都會隨身攜帶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.26,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢  雖然確實是加奈不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.51,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過希望你不要生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.81,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於加奈來說\N護身符真的是攸關生死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.49,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:40.76,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野是那個Black Manta的駕駛員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.81,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手腕嵌著金屬球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:48.94,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會突然留鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.17,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至頭髮一下子變白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.77,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在眼睛也看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:55.78,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是因為伊里野是\NBlack Manta的駕駛員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.23,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無人知曉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.33,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野在和敵人戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.97,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事大人來做  不就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:09.79,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你們擅自引發的戰爭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.81,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那種事一定要讓伊里野來做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:17.00,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有伊里野要這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.96,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口插滿針筒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.34,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿身是血地倒在這裡不可啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:25.03,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:34.18,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺羽同學  我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宰了你  這個臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.07,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.27,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻在這裡信口開河
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:57.57,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝得一副只有自己才理解加奈的嘴臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:02.46,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  你到底都知道加奈的什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:07.38,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無知者的善意根本就是不負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:10.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就只有餵野貓的覺悟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.37,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把加奈送回保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:36.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會…接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:23.78,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:27.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍵盤上的鼠標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:29.59,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書架上的布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:33.77,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是社長的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:36.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:38.61,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:40.12,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:41.87,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為燈亮著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:46.29,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:48.21,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:51.64,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:23:01.92,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今…都沒有…一次都…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:08.85,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符什麼的…沒有…想…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:11.11,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:18.23,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要過…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:23.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:26.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長馬上就會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:29.14,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長的話  一定能做些什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:31.41,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長什麼都會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.00,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野的事情也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:45.68,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:46.93,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:49.26,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長？ 是社長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:50.52,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在人在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:51.25,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話亭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:52.76,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.47,0:23:55.10,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊情況很嚴重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:57.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  這裡也很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.55,0:23:58.71,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:00.04,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是生物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.77,0:24:01.91,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:02.86,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:05.22,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺羽特派員 那是生物！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:08.82,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.93,0:24:10.91,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園原電波新聞社不會向鎮壓屈服！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:13.02,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有報導自由…！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.12,0:24:14.61,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了！  你們這群混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.59,0:24:26.20,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.14,0:24:30.72,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我不會問第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.62,0:24:35.41,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要現在馬上回去基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:38.67,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是希望讓我來幫你？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.49,0:24:54.08,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺羽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.74,0:24:55.50,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.60,0:24:58.28,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起伊里野不用再回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.36,0:25:01.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到伊里野自己想回去的時候再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.01,0:25:05.74,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  馬上就會被抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.46,0:25:08.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  我會和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.17,0:25:09.67,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.14,0:25:10.76,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.21,0:25:13.54,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為淺羽身上有蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.31,0:25:20.73,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電池蟲和電波蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.04,0:25:23.70,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載有發信芯片的生化植入系統
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.04,0:25:23.70,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(252,441)\fs20}transponder chip
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.04,0:25:23.70,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(414,441)\fs20}bioimplant
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.74,0:25:30.55,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…會被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.46,0:25:36.04,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.90,0:25:37.90,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.67,0:25:51.98,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺羽  痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.87,0:25:53.93,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.26,0:25:56.39,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事


